data.description: Welcome to this exceptional quadplex nestled in the heart of Decatur, offering an incredible opportunity for investors or those looking to live in one unit and generate rental income from the others. Each unit features 1 spacious bedroom, a well-appointed bathroom, a cozy living room, and a fully-equipped kitchen. Meticulously maintained, this property boasts modern amenities while preserving its historic charm. **Key Features:** - Updated kitchens with stainless steel appliances - Hardwood floors throughout - Ample natural light in each unit - Private entrance for each apartment - laundry closet in each unit **Location:** Situated in the highly sought-after Decatur area, this quadplex is conveniently located near shops, restaurants, parks, and public transportation. Enjoy the vibrant community and the ease of access to downtown Decatur, Emory University, and major highways for quick commutes. **Investment Potential:** This property presents an excellent investment opportunity with strong rental demand. Decatur's thriving rental market makes this quadplex an attractive option for investors seeking steady returns. QUALIFIED BUYERS ONLY, PLEASE! Do not visit property or disturb tenants. Prior to showing request, please forward proof of funds/pre-approval letter by email.
